WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.041 --> 00:00:01.251
In just the USA.

00:00:01.251 --> 00:00:04.796
Over 150 million people
have limited transportation.

00:00:04.879 --> 00:00:06.673
That's almost
half the population.

00:00:06.673 --> 00:00:08.925
And in even poorer countries
around the world,

00:00:08.925 --> 00:00:11.261
lack of transportation
is even higher.

00:00:11.261 --> 00:00:14.139
A year ago, when we found out
about the shortage of sanitary

00:00:14.139 --> 00:00:15.473
drinking water in Kenya,

00:00:15.473 --> 00:00:17.642
we distributed
dozens of Lectric eBikes

00:00:17.642 --> 00:00:18.852
to water deliverymen

00:00:18.852 --> 00:00:21.396
who used to push their heavily
loaded bicycles over

00:00:21.396 --> 00:00:24.607
ten miles around the city
just to make $7 a day.

00:00:24.983 --> 00:00:25.984
With their new bikes,

00:00:25.984 --> 00:00:28.778
they are now able to do
a lot more trips per day,

00:00:28.803 --> 00:00:31.798
which leads to significantly
more income for their families.

00:00:32.157 --> 00:00:33.867
You have made work easier.

00:00:33.867 --> 00:00:36.786
And after seeing the profound
impact it had on the community,

00:00:36.786 --> 00:00:38.913
we went to our partners
at Lectric eBikes

00:00:38.913 --> 00:00:40.206
to see if they
wanted to help us.

00:00:40.206 --> 00:00:43.209
Seeing how they sponsored 13 of
our Beast Philanthropy videos.

00:00:43.209 --> 00:00:44.711
I don't think you'll be shocked
to hear

00:00:44.711 --> 00:00:48.757
that they donated $600,000
worth of Lectric eBikes

00:00:48.965 --> 00:00:51.634
We then asked you guys
to nominate a person you knew

00:00:51.634 --> 00:00:54.095
that was in need of life
changing transportation.

00:00:54.095 --> 00:00:55.805
And after receiving
thousands of videos

00:00:55.805 --> 00:00:57.307
of amazing people in need.

00:00:57.307 --> 00:01:00.101
We were so excited to start
giving them away.

00:01:00.101 --> 00:01:02.020
This e-bike
would change my life.

00:01:02.020 --> 00:01:05.273
That will help me and my husband
so much.

00:01:05.315 --> 00:01:06.900
We're kicking off this massive

00:01:06.900 --> 00:01:08.943
giveaway
right here in North Carolina

00:01:08.943 --> 00:01:12.547
where Darren will give away
the first of over 600 bikes.

00:01:13.281 --> 00:01:14.407
This is Maria,

00:01:14.407 --> 00:01:16.743
a single mother
of two children who works

00:01:16.743 --> 00:01:19.287
 for 14 hours a day
washing dishes only

00:01:19.287 --> 00:01:21.456
to send the little pay
she has back to her

00:01:21.456 --> 00:01:22.791
children in Guatemala,

00:01:22.791 --> 00:01:24.626
who she hasn't seen in years.

00:01:24.774 --> 00:01:26.774
I have been here for a long time.

00:01:27.047 --> 00:01:28.523
It's been 5 years now.

00:01:30.465 --> 00:01:32.258
And on top of her
long working hours,

00:01:32.258 --> 00:01:35.220
she still has to walk
for miles every single day

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:36.763
just to get to
and from work.

00:01:36.971 --> 00:01:38.973
This is the first of
hundreds of bikes

00:01:38.973 --> 00:01:40.934
that we're going to be
giving away across the country.

00:01:40.934 --> 00:01:42.936
And because this is
the first one,

00:01:42.936 --> 00:01:46.648
we're going to surprise Maria
with an extra $5,000 in cash.

00:01:47.440 --> 00:01:49.776
Okay, Let's go surprise her.

00:01:50.902 --> 00:01:52.779
We got you a present.

00:01:55.865 --> 00:01:57.575
Maria told us
she donates whatever

00:01:57.575 --> 00:02:00.578
she has left to feed poor kids
from her village back home.

00:02:00.787 --> 00:02:03.456
So on top of the $5,000,
we surprised her

00:02:03.456 --> 00:02:05.667
with an additional
$7,000

00:02:06.104 --> 00:02:08.837
so that she can help her
village in Guatemala.

00:02:08.837 --> 00:02:10.755
With this new bike,
Maria can easily

00:02:10.755 --> 00:02:12.924
get to and from work
in only 10 minutes,

00:02:12.924 --> 00:02:14.968
not being able
to get to work

00:02:14.968 --> 00:02:15.969
or to get to school

00:02:15.969 --> 00:02:17.470
or to get to your
medical appointments.

00:02:17.470 --> 00:02:20.515
It exacerbates the problems
that people face

00:02:20.515 --> 00:02:21.349
and it keeps them

00:02:21.349 --> 00:02:23.935
trapped in the circumstances
that they are in.

00:02:23.935 --> 00:02:25.603
Now, if you
thought that was special.

00:02:25.603 --> 00:02:28.022
we still have
599 more to go.

