their entire lives

00:04:04.869 --> 00:04:07.330
to support thousands of refugees
and provide them

00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:09.707
with the necessities
they need to live a normal life.

00:04:09.707 --> 00:04:11.960
They've left their culture.
They've left their language.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.378
They've left their families.

00:04:13.378 --> 00:04:16.506
And we see them probably
at one of the lowest points

00:04:16.506 --> 00:04:17.382
